trans-unit.source: Provides a read-only collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> objects.

The TransformerTypeCollection class represents a read-only collection of objects, typically used by <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> objects to manage sets of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects.

A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control uses a TransformerTypeCollection collection to keep a list of available <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects on a page, whereas a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> object uses a TransformerTypeCollection collection to track the available <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects that it contains.
Although the TransformerTypeCollection collection is read-only, you can make programmatic changes to the properties of the underlying controls referenced in the collection.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection"></xref> class with no members in the collection.

Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection"></xref> class containing the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> objects.
A collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> objects.
transformerTypes contains objects that are not transformers.

Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection"></xref> class by combining an existing <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection"></xref> collection with the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> objects.

A collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> objects already contained in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection"></xref>.
A collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> objects to combine with the collection in the `existingTransformerTypes` parameter.
transformerTypes contains objects that are not transformers.
Returns a value indicating whether a particular transformer exists in the collection.

The Contains method enables you to check a particular <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> object and determine whether it is part of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> collection.
A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> that is checked to determine whether it is in the collection.
A Boolean value that indicates whether a particular transformer is in the collection.
Copies the collection to an array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> objects.

The CopyTo method is useful when you want to assemble a custom array that can contain all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> collection, a subset of those objects, or a superset of those objects.
An array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> objects to contain the copied collection.
The starting point in the array at which to place the collection contents.
Creates a collection for storing transformers.
The Empty field creates and returns a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> object.
The instance is created through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection.%23ctor%2A> constructor and does not contain any existing members in the collection.
To be added.
Returns the position of a particular member in the collection.
A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> that is a member of the collection.
An integer that indicates the position of a particular object in the collection.
Gets a member of the collection based on its position in the collection.
The index of a particular <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> in a collection.
The located at index.
